sequenceDiagram
    participant browser
    participant server

    browser->>server: GET <website address>
    activate server
    server->>browser: returns the webpage HTML
    deactivate server

    browser->>server: GET <script address>
    activate server
    server->>browser: returns the JavaScript-file used by the site
    deactivate server

    browser->>server: GET <stylesheet address>
    activate server
    server->>browser: returns the CSS-file
    deactivate server

    browser->>server: GET <data address>
    activate server
    server->>browser: returns the note data as JSON
    deactivate server
